{"tid":1292565,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"安徽大媽衝紅燈被拍 螢幕公開個人資料被嚇窒","createTime":"2019-07-07T11:22:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T09:58:12.000Z","uid":68738,"like":98,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"83a42c9b8ab991c0174d511b7465bdbb76c1d768","tid":1292565,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T11:22:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2019/06/20190602_pl_%E5%A4%A7%E5%AA%BD_fb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2019%2F06%2F20190602_pl_%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AA%25BD_fb.jpg&h=1056d462&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然「馬路如虎口」，但不少途人仍然會趁沒有車便衝紅燈。為了防止胡亂過馬路的情況，近日安徽省實施「行人闖紅燈抓拍系統」，當有市民違規衝紅燈，就會被系統拍下照片，並會在馬路旁邊的螢幕上公開其個人資料。<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2019/06/20190602_pl_%E8%A1%8C%E4%BA%BA3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2019%2F06%2F20190602_pl_%25E8%25A1%258C%25E4%25BA%25BA3.jpg&h=53df0083&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網上有一條流傳的片段，有一名衝紅燈的大媽被拍下，她的長相及個人資料立刻登上電子大螢幕，大媽看到後嚇得說不出話來，呆站在原地長達1分鐘。<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2019/06/20190602_pl_%E8%A1%8C%E4%BA%BA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2019%2F06%2F20190602_pl_%25E8%25A1%258C%25E4%25BA%25BA.jpg&h=25315050&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當地警方表示，此設施是為了維護市區道路秩序，更強調資料除了在電子螢幕上顯示，更會定期把違規行人的資料上存至微博，以加強阻嚇性，警員更稱會對這位闖紅燈的大媽進行教育。<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2019/06/20190602_pl_%E8%A1%8C%E4%BA%BA4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2019%2F06%2F20190602_pl_%25E8%25A1%258C%25E4%25BA%25BA4.jpg&h=591a099a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好撚痴線<